snippet: The couple graduated from the University of Michigan, where they met.
lead_paragraph: Jessica Rachel Levy, the daughter of Valerie and Edward Levy of North Caldwell, N.J., was married Saturday to Eric Bradley Farkas, the son of Susan Wertheim Farkas and Ervi Farkas of Plainview, N.Y. Cantor Wayne S. Siet officiated at Natirar, an estate and events venue in Peapack, N.J. The bride, 28, and the bridegroom, 27, graduated from the University of Michigan, where they met.
